nodes.text: "The Fist of the Empire" is a four-page magazine article written by Megan Crouse and published in Star Wars Insider 177 on November 28, 2018. It features an interview with Janina Gavankar, who portrayed Iden Versio in the video game Star Wars Battlefront II. The article was later reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2019.
